    <article class="legal">
      <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: June 21, 2026</p>

      <p>These Terms govern your use of the website at <strong>telcoos.io</strong> (the “Site”), operated by TelcoOS (“we,” “us”). By using the Site, you agree to these Terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the Site.</p>

