      <p>The Site’s content, design, and branding — including the TelcoOS name and logo — are owned by us or our licensors. You may not copy, reproduce, or use them without our prior written permission.</p>

      <h2>Product descriptions and roadmap</h2>
      <p>Descriptions of TelcoOS on the Site, including any “roadmap” or “in development” items, are provided for information only, may change without notice, and are not commitments, guarantees, or offers.</p>

      <h2>No warranty</h2>
